      <title>特朗普公民身份限制在早些时候暂停后被无限期阻止</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/second-us-judge-blocks-trump-birthright-citizenship-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马里兰州一名联邦法官阻止了唐纳德·特朗普总统限制自动出生公民权的举动，这对特朗普在推翻一个多世纪以来美国法律和法庭判例的广泛移民打击行动中造成了又一次法律挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/second-us-judge-blocks-trump-birthright-citizenship-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 16:17:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将公布特朗普结束乌克兰三年战争的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-set-to-present-trump-s-plan-for-peace-in-ukraine-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国盟友预计，唐纳德·特朗普总统的政府将在下周德国慕尼黑安全会议上提出一项期待已久的结束俄罗斯对乌克兰战争的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-set-to-present-trump-s-plan-for-peace-in-ukraine-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 16:03:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工会请求法院阻止财政部向马斯克的 DOGE 提供数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/treasury-musk-s-doge-targeted-by-union-request-to-block-data-access</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群工会要求法院下达临时命令，禁止美国财政部将美国人的个人和财务数据移交给与伊隆马斯克的政府效率执法团队有关的人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/treasury-musk-s-doge-targeted-by-union-request-to-block-data-access</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:42:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电视直播内阁争吵导致哥伦比亚政府动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/colombia-s-government-shaken-after-televised-cabinet-quarrel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚政府在一次电视转播的内阁会议上陷入混乱，会议变成了充满泪水的相互指责和争吵，导致一位部长建议全体部长辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/colombia-s-government-shaken-after-televised-cabinet-quarrel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:34:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国邮政局撤销暂停向中国发货的决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-postal-service-says-it-s-accepting-china-hong-kong-packages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国邮政局表示，将接受来自中国内地和香港的“所有国际入境邮件和包裹”，撤回了几个小时前宣布的暂停部分海外货运的公告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-postal-service-says-it-s-accepting-china-hong-kong-packages</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼提议取消加拿大资本利得税上调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/carney-to-propose-scrapping-canada-s-capital-gains-tax-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼周三表示，如果赢得自由党领袖竞选并成为加拿大总理，他将取消增加加拿大资本利得税的提议，并推出中产阶级减税措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/carney-to-propose-scrapping-canada-s-capital-gains-tax-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非在解决医疗保险僵局方面取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/south-africa-signals-breakthrough-in-health-insurance-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府表示，其在解决新国家医疗保险计划僵局方面正在取得进展，批评人士称该计划将侵犯患者和医护人员的权利，并使私营部门受到边缘化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/south-africa-signals-breakthrough-in-health-insurance-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 10:47:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和马斯克争夺国会权力，压倒共和党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gop-lawmakers-cede-to-trump-musk-power-grab-without-a-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当唐纳德·特朗普总统发起一场历史性的扩大行政权力的行动时，国会共和党人几乎没发出任何声音，特朗普的行动一路压倒了他们，并在整个联邦政府中引发了焦虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gop-lawmakers-cede-to-trump-musk-power-grab-without-a-challenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
